{"tid":2255631,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"意漢涉10年間160次強姦性侵親女及多名女童　在法國落網","createTime":"2020-10-23T16:55:47.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-23T17:14:55.000Z","uid":295230,"like":1,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"0212e11e0e5d9c7aaceab483e2b892fa58a8f768","tid":2255631,"uid":295230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-23T16:55:47.000Z","msg":"法國拘捕一名被德國通緝的意大利男子，他被指涉嫌10年間多次強姦親女等多名女童，涉及160項強姦或性侵指控。<br />\n<br />\n法國拘捕一名被德國通緝的意大利男子，他被指涉嫌10年間多次強姦親女等多名女童，涉及160項強姦或性侵指控。<br />\n<br />\n法國上周五（16日）依據歐洲的通緝令，在德國邊境附近、法國斯特拉斯堡（Strasbourg）以南地區拘捕涉案52歲意大利男子。他被指自2000年起的10年間多次強姦親生女兒，其間亦涉嫌強姦女友的女兒等多名女童。<br />\n<br />\n德國警方去年10月初獲悉疑犯從德國飛赴法國東部，通告法國當局，要求把他通緝歸案。疑犯於女友家中落網，目前被扣押，將移交德國當局。"},{"pid":"8064bfd20703560b3e511440fcb1f7e86563b77e","tid":2255631,"uid":295230,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-23T16:55:52.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%e5%9c%8b%e9%9a%9b/article/20201023/s00005/1603450471663/%e6%84%8f%e6%bc%a2%e6%b6%8910%e5%b9%b4%e9%96%93160%e6%ac%a1%e5%bc%b7%e5%a7%a6%e6%80%a7%e4%be%b5%e8%a6%aa%e5%a5%b3%e5%8f%8a%e5%a4%9a%e5%90%8d%e5%a5%b3%e7%ab%a5-%e5%9c%a8%e6%b3%95%e5%9c%8b%e8%90%bd%e7%b6%b2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25e5%259c%258b%25e9%259a%259b%2Farticle%2F20201023%2Fs00005%2F1603450471663%2F%25e6%2584%258f%25e6%25bc%25a2%25e6%25b6%258910%25e5%25b9%25b4%25e9%2596%2593160%25e6%25ac%25a1%25e5%25bc%25b7%25e5%25a7%25a6%25e6%2580%25a7%25e4%25be%25b5%25e8%25a6%25aa%25e5%25a5%25b3%25e5%258f%258a%25e5%25a4%259a%25e5%2590%258d%25e5%25a5%25b3%25e7%25ab%25a5-%25e5%259c%25a8%25e6%25b3%2595%25e5%259c%258b%25e8%2590%25bd%25e7%25b6%25b2&d=Z0jJ2Ci5UPqU8nDHOGo4vOIs%2Fr43DZ9KHrtYDEqBsnw%3D&h=3677a695\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25e5%259c%258b%25e9%259a%259b%2Farticle%2F20201023%2Fs00005%2F1603450471663%2F%25e6%2584%258f%25e6%25bc%25a2%25e6%25b6%258910%25e5%25b9%25b4%25e9%2596%2593160%25e6%25ac%25a1%25e5%